QuestData.Title: Muckgill's Flipper or Something...
QuestData.Description: This looks like Muckgill's flipper or something. Maybe there's somebody that cares that you killed this murloc back at the Azurelode Mine camp. Probably not, but it's worth a shot.$B$BTake Muckgill's fin or whatever it might be back to Captain Keyton at the Azurelode Mine in southwestern Hillsbrad.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver Muckgill's Flipper back to Captain Keyton at the Azurelode Mine in Hillsbrad Foothills.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do I look like some kind of murloc scientist?
QuestData.RewardText: Muckgill you say? Never heard of him. What is this anyway? Some kind of fin or something?
